.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, roller, car
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport         | car | subway    | roller  | boat    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

