The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, zombie
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, horse, snake
City: colone, prague, berlin, london
1. the person watching drama movies is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to colone##2
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to berlin and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | drama   | documentary | satire |
| Pet           | cat       | horse   | frog        | snake  |
| City     | berlin | prague | colone         | london |

