.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cherry, cucumber, kale
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hamster
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, singing, drawing
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry  | cucumber | kale     | carrot     |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | goat     | guinea-pig |
| Hobby       | skydiving  | drawing   | chess | singing    |
| Transport   | train   | subway   | jet-ski  | van        |

