 4. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is between the fan of r&b and the person who's birthday is in december##2
10. the person watching spy movies is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
